<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      /* Inline CSS styles go here */
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <table
      align="center"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      width="600"
      style="border-collapse: collapse; background-color: #ffffff; margin: 20px auto; border: 1px solid #dddddd;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0; background-color: #014ab1;">
          <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px;">Welcome to Our Platform!</h1>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; color: #333333;">
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Hi <%= name %>,</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">
            We’re so excited to have you on board. Here’s to embarking on a journey filled with opportunities and
            excitement.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">
            To get started, make sure to explore our platform and set up your profile.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 10px;">
            If you have any questions or need support, we’re here to help every step of the way.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px;">
          <a
            href="<%= loginUrl %>"
            style="
              display: inline-block;
              text-decoration: none;
              background-color: #00f6d1;
              color: #ffffff;
              padding: 10px 20px;
              font-size: 16px;
              border-radius: 5px;
              margin-top: 10px;
            "
            >Verify Your Email</a
          >
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; line-height: 1.6;">
          <p style="margin: 0;">
            If you didn’t create an account with us, please ignore this email. You won’t receive any further
            communication.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0;">Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 10px; background-color: #014ab1; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px;">
          <p style="margin: 0;">&copy;  Our Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
